OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fwill continue to bring showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain overnight, and a
OL,8,Fmixture of low cloud and fog leading
OL,9,Fto poor driving conditions,
OL,10,Fparticularly over the hills. Staying
OL,11,Ffrost free under the blanket of cloud.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA cloudy and grey start with
OL,14,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain. Skies
OL,15,Fwill brighten a little later on with
OL,16,Fsome hazy spells of sunshine possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
